{
  "id": "69f8546b52bf3c50f22e4aba",
  "title": "ハイパーテキストガーデン",
  "created": 1777882238,
  "updated": 1777883553,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f8546b52bf3c50f22e4aba",
      "text": "ハイパーテキストガーデン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882238,
      "updated": 1777882238
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547e0000000000d569aa",
      "text": "　ブログやSNSのような時系列の更新ではなく、知識やアイデアを庭のように育て、関連付ける公開スペース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882238,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569ab",
      "text": " マーク・バーンスタイン（Mark Bernstein）が[1998年]に提唱",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882279
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569ac",
      "text": "　庭（Garden）のような管理",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569ad",
      "text": "　　一度に完成させるのではなく、アイデアを少しずつ書き加え、リンクで繋ぎ、時間をかけて「育てる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882297
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569ae",
      "text": "　非時系列",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569af",
      "text": "　　ブログ（日記）と異なり、最新記事が常に上位に来るわけではなく、関連する情報が構造化される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882302
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b0",
      "text": "　[セレンディピティ]（偶然の発見）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882546
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b1",
      "text": "　　探索的にWebを歩き回り、興味深い情報に出会う体験を重視する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882308
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b2",
      "text": " [hypertext garden]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b4",
      "text": " [デジタルガーデン]（[digital garden]） - ほぼ同意義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b5",
      "text": " [エバーグリーンノート]（[evergreen notes]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777882239
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b6",
      "text": " [ハイパーテキスト]（[hypertext]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777883553
    },
    {
      "id": "69f8547f0000000000d569b7",
      "text": " [パーソナルナレッジマネジメント]（[personal knowledge management]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777882239,
      "updated": 1777883532
    },
